运行这个代码需要用到makefile文件
1. 在终端内输入 make， 回车
2. 然后再输入 make run, 回车， 就可以开始程序了
3. 按照程序内的提示来操作
4. 输入"kaigua"解锁开挂模式， 但是开挂模式时不能输入666，因为我写代码的时候偷懒了，至于为什么，你仔细看就懂了
注意默认的版本是中文版

To run the program: 
1. in the command line, type "make chouka.out" to make executables
2. then type "./chouka.out" to run the executable. 
(Since the default run rule in Makefile runs the Chinese version, you can't use Makefile's rule to run the executable)
3. then follow the instructions in the program
4. enter "kaigua" can switch to the kaigua (literally means "cheat" in Chinese) 
mode where you can do any amount of wishes as you like except to 666. If you wonder why, you can check out the source code.

